<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>한서 E출석부</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style_classCheck.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <div class="top-bar">
    <span>한서 E출석부</span>
    <div class="top-right">
      <span id="today-date"></span>
      <button class="logout-btn" onclick="logout()">로그아웃</button>
    </div>
  </div>
<!-- 다 임의로 넣음-->
<div class="sidebar">
  <!--<img src="professor.jpg" alt="Professor" class="professor-img">-->
  <span id="professorname"></span>
  <p class="semester-info">2025학년도 1학기</p>
  <h3>- 담당 강의 선택</h3>
  <select class="lecture-select" onchange="lectureSelected()">
    <option value="">강의를 선택하세요</option>
  </select>
  <a href="#" class="course-application-link" onclick="openCourseApplication()">- 강의 신청</a>
</div>

<div class="content">
  <h2>환영합니다!</h2>
  <p>강의를 선택하면 이곳에 상세 정보가 표시됩니다.</p>
</div>


  <!-- 출석 확인 모달 -->
  <div id="attendanceModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <span class="close" onclick="closeAttendancePopup()">&times;</span>
      <h2 id="modal-title">학생 출석 확인</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>주차</th>
            <th>출결 상태</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="attendanceBody">
          <!-- 1주차 ~ 16주차 행은 JS에서 동적으로 생성 -->
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="script_classCheck.js"></script>
</body>
</html>